short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension will help to manage and use various web URLs from a single HTML page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension contains one HTML file which can be downloaded. Download the file and edit required web URLs to your desired URLs. By default all URLs are added as "https://www.google.com/". There are total 7 pagination pages in this HTML and each page contains 70 URLs. So total 490 URLs you can store and manage. After clicking on a URL it will open URL address in a new tab.
